Redesign:
- Consumer side now uses a Find My-style floating capsule at the
  bottom, drag up through three snap heights
- Unified tab bar (Explore / Favorites / Notifications / Profile)
  built into the capsule — switching tabs no longer collapses the
  sheet or navigates away
- All four sections live inside the same capsule, no page transitions
- Vendor category menu simplified; search moved to the bottom of
  explore
- Long-press a favorite to unsubscribe; QR subscribe moved into
  favorites
- Gear icon in each section header opens a settings sheet
  (notifications / feedback / privacy / about)
